title: Microsoft Office 2016 VL x86 Spanish Language Accessory Pack
description:
You can install language accessory packs after installing Microsoft Office, to add additional display, help, or proofing tools.
This ISO file includes: Language Pack, LIPs and Proofing Tools for the core applications (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, OneNote, Outlook, Publisher, Access and Skype for Business).

Requirements
---------------

Microsoft Office 2016 Volume License (x86)
This Language Accessory Pack is NOT compatible with Office 2016 Office 365 / Click-to-Run

Installation and configuration: please read included About text file
